## The future of capturing and publishing KPIs for MmS
As mentioned previously, we will need to monitor and track a range of KPIs during the private beta. However, we also should prepare for what metrics we should track in later stages of the project.

#### Post-MVP KPIs will include:
* Number of times event history accordion opened - if more than (x%) of time, should it be an accordion?
* Time between ephemeris upload and analysis being generated and uploaded
* Time between analysis being completed and the Time of Closest Approach (TCA)
* The number of API requests
* User journeys (heat maps)

